name: SYNTHCITY - Fisherman
description:
LOCATION: CATFISH MARKET

“The Fisherman is an ominous being often found around CATFISH MARKET. It uses VPN's to cloak itself, making it hard to distinguish what or who the Fisherman actually is. Rumour has it that when it reveals its true identity to someone, misfortune will follow that person for sure.”

By Die-Jay-Cee
